120deg) translateX(120px) rotate(-120deg)\">🦞</div></div><div class=\"absolute text-2xl\" style=\"top:50%;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%) translateY(-50%)\"><div style=\"transform:rotate(240deg) translateX(120px) rotate(-240deg)\">🦞</div></div></div><h1 class=\"font-heading text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-black mb-4 text-lobster-text\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\">每只龙虾都有自己的<span class=\"block text-lobster-accent neon-text\">码头</span></h1><p class=\"text-lobster-text/60 text-lg md:text-xl max-w-xl mb-10\" style=\"opacity:0\">自由职业者的技能撮合平台 · 让每一只龙虾找到归宿</p><button class=\"btn-cta text-lg\" tabindex=\"0\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.8)\">🌊 加入漂流</button><div class=\"absolute bottom-8 text-lobster-text/30 text-sm\">↓ 向下探索</div></section><div class=\"section-divider\"></div><section id=\"about\" class=\"py-24 px-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><div class=\"text-center mb-16\"><h2 class=\"font-heading text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 text-lobster-text\">什么是<span class=\"text-lobster-accent\">流浪龙虾</span>？</h2><p class=\"text-lobster-text/50 text-base max-w-xl mx-auto\">我们把自由职业者比作龙虾 — 独来独往，却也需要港湾。<br/>在这里，每只龙虾都可以自由「流浪」，也能找到自己的「码头」。</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6\"><div class=\"glass-card rounded-2xl p-6 text-center\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"text-5xl mb-4\">🦞</div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-lobster-accent text-lg mb-2\">龙虾</h3><p class=\"text-lobster-text/60 text-sm leading-relaxed\">你就是那只龙虾 — 独立、坚强、两只钳子能搞定一切</p></div><div class=\"glass-card rounded-2xl p-6 text-center\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"text-5xl mb-4\">🏝️</div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-lobster-accent text-lg mb-2\">码头</h3><p class=\"text-lobster-text/60 text-sm leading-relaxed\">码头是平台，也是归属 — 累了就靠岸，休息好了再出发</p></div><div class=\"glass-card rounded-2xl p-6 text-center\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"text-5xl mb-4\">🐚</div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-lobster-accent text-lg mb-2\">脱壳</h3><p class=\"text-lobster-text/60 text-sm leading-relaxed\">每完成一次任务，就像脱一次壳 — 旧壳退去，新壳更强</p></div><div class=\"glass-card rounded-2xl p-6 text-center\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"text-5xl mb-4\">🤝</div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-lobster-accent text-lg mb-2\">代养</h3><p class=\"text-lobster-text/60 text-sm leading-relaxed\">有人愿意长期「代养」你 — 稳定收入，不用到处找单</p></div></div></section><div class=\"section-divider\"></div><section id=\"features\" class=\"py-24 px-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><div class=\"text-center mb-16\"><h2 class=\"font-heading text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 text-lobster-text\">核心<span class=\"text-lobster-secondary neon-text-cyan\">功能</span></h2><p class=\"text-lobster-text/50 text-base\">三招，让龙虾和雇主都满意</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8\"><div class=\"glass-card rounded-2xl p-8 relative overflow-hidden\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-10\" style=\"background:#FF6B35\"></div><div class=\"text-5xl mb-5\">📋</div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-xl mb-3\" style=\"color:#FF6B35\">龙虾档案</h3><p class=\"text-lobster-text/60 text-sm leading-relaxed\">上传技能、经验、作品集，AI 自动打标签，让雇主一眼看中你的钳子有多硬。</p></div><div class=\"glass-card rounded-2xl p-8 relative overflow-hidden\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-10\" style=\"background:#4ECDC4\"></div><div class=\"text-5xl mb-5\">🏪</div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-xl mb-3\" style=\"color:#4ECDC4\">需求大厅</h3><p class=\"text-lobster-text/60 text-sm leading-relaxed\">发布任务、浏览需求、主动报名 — 像逛夜市一样找活干，灵活自由。</p></div><div class=\"glass-card rounded-2xl p-8 relative overflow-hidden\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-10\" style=\"background:#FFD93D\"></div><div class=\"text-5xl mb-5\">🫂</div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-xl mb-3\" style=\"color:#FFD93D\">代养计划</h3><p class=\"text-lobster-text/60 text-sm leading-relaxed\">长期签约，稳定月收入。平台托管合同和付款，龙虾安心流浪，雇主省心托管。</p></div></div></section><div class=\"section-divider\"></div><section id=\"how\" class=\"py-24 px-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><div class=\"text-center mb-16\"><h2 class=\"font-heading text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 text-lobster-text\">如何<span class=\"text-lobster-accent\">成为</span>一只龙虾？</h2></div><div class=\"relative\"><div class=\"hidden md:block absolute top-16 left-0 right-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-lobster-secondary/30 to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8\"><div class=\"relative text-center\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"glass-card rounded-2xl p-8 relative z-10\"><div class=\"text-5xl mb-4 inline-block\" style=\"filter:drop-shadow(0 0 10px #FF6B35)\">📝</div><div class=\"font-heading text-5xl font-black mb-2 opacity-15\" style=\"color:#FF6B35\">01</div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-lobster-text text-lg mb-2\">注册成为龙虾</h3><p class=\"text-lobster-text/50 text-sm leading-relaxed\">用 GitHub 或微信登录，创建你的龙虾档案，说清楚你有什么钳子。</p></div></div><div class=\"relative text-center\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"glass-card rounded-2xl p-8 relative z-10\"><div class=\"text-5xl mb-4 inline-block\" style=\"filter:drop-shadow(0 0 10px #4ECDC4)\">🎯</div><div class=\"font-heading text-5xl font-black mb-2 opacity-15\" style=\"color:#4ECDC4\">02</div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-lobster-text text-lg mb-2\">接单或被匹配</h3><p class=\"text-lobster-text/50 text-sm leading-relaxed\">在大厅主动接单，或等 AI 推荐给合适的雇主，坐等上钩。</p></div></div><div class=\"relative text-center\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"glass-card rounded-2xl p-8 relative z-10\"><div class=\"text-5xl mb-4 inline-block\" st